Sentencas: Nanocrystalline, uniform, dense, and adherent cerium oxide (CeO2) thin films have been successfully deposited by a simple and cost effective spray pyrolysis technique.
Titulo: Structural, morphological and electrical properties of spray deposited nano-crystalline CeO2 thin films

Sentencas: CeO2 films were deposited at low substrate and annealing temperatures of 350 degrees C and 500 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Structural, morphological and electrical properties of spray deposited nano-crystalline CeO2 thin films

Sentencas: Films were characterized by differential thermal analysis, X-ray diffraction, scanning electron microscopy, atomic force microscopy; two probe resistivity method and impedance spectroscopy.
Titulo: Structural, morphological and electrical properties of spray deposited nano-crystalline CeO2 thin films

Sentencas: X-ray diffraction analysis revealed the formation of single phase, well crystalline thin films with cubic fluorite structure.
Titulo: Structural, morphological and electrical properties of spray deposited nano-crystalline CeO2 thin films

Sentencas: Crystallite size was found to be in the range of 10-15 nm.
Titulo: Structural, morphological and electrical properties of spray deposited nano-crystalline CeO2 thin films

Sentencas: AFM showed formation of smooth films with morphological grain size 27 nm.
Titulo: Structural, morphological and electrical properties of spray deposited nano-crystalline CeO2 thin films

Sentencas: Films were found to be highly resistive with room temperature resistivity of the order of 10(2) Omega cm.
Titulo: Structural, morphological and electrical properties of spray deposited nano-crystalline CeO2 thin films

Sentencas: Activation energy was calculated and found to be 0.78 eV.
Titulo: Structural, morphological and electrical properties of spray deposited nano-crystalline CeO2 thin films

Sentencas: The deposited film showed high oxygen ion conductivity of 5.94 x 10(-3) S cm(-1) at 350 degrees C. Thus, the deposited material shows a potential application in intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFC) and might be useful for mu-SOFC and industrial catalyst applications.
Titulo: Structural, morphological and electrical properties of spray deposited nano-crystalline CeO2 thin films
Structural, morphological and electrical properties of spray deposited nano-crystalline CeO2 thin films
Structural, morphological and electrical properties of spray deposited nano-crystalline CeO2 thin films
